Silly silly escape sequence wrapper

Author: Jimmy Kumpulainen (yelo at yaoi dot se)

Ex: import escc

    tc = escc.escapeColors()
    tc.textcolor(bg="BLUE", fgmode="BLINK", fg="GREEN")
    print("This is just another sample string")
    tc.reset()

In a perfect world this would print the sample string in green with a
blue background, and make the text blink, then reset the output to normal.

TO-DO: exceptions, make it failsafe
